items.sentence: I wonder who the people I saw Tom with were.

I'm not sure that Tom knows what he's doing.
I'm satisfied with the results of the exams.
I'm not a child. Don't talk to me like I am.
I'm glad things worked out the way they did.
I'm going to get some grub and I'll be back.
I'm looking for a gift for a friend of mine.
How did you know that I needed one of these?
Everyone here knows that we can't trust Tom.
Didn't you know Tom and I needed to do that?
Did you know Tom had a house on Park Street?
Did Tom know that you were going to do that?
I know Tom will be allowed to do that again.
I know Tom wasn't the only one who did that.
